  'Applications must be submitted online at: eThekwini Municipality Bursary Application 2025 (Reference Number: ETH250401-3) Enter “www.zabursaries.co.za” in the field asking how you heard about the eThekwini Municipality bursary. Submit clear copies of the following supporting documentation along with your completed online application (the submission of these documents is compulsory – if any items are missing, your application may be disqualified): ID document (certified copy) Matric certificate (certified copy) Full academic record, if in 2nd or higher year of study (on tertiary letterhead) Proof of university registration, if in your 1st year of study (on tertiary letterhead)',
