  'https://www.labour.gov.za/DocumentCenter/Publications/Compensation%20for%20Occupational%20Injuries%20and%20Diseases/CF%20External%20Bursary%20Application%20Form%202026.pdf',
  'https://www.zabursaries.co.za/government-bursaries-south-africa/compensation-fund-bursary/',
